fields.description: Belffin modular couch is a modern designed couch with tons of features like adjustable armrest/backrest, built in storage space underneath, customized configurations. You can easily add or move around the sections to fit your space. The velvet fabric is both comfortable and easy to take care of. Each box comes with a clear instruction manual, very easy to put together on your own.
name: Belffin Modular Velvet Tufted Pull-out Oversized U Shaped Sectional Sofa Couch with Storage Chaises
